      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an unparalleled E46 M3, a purist\u2019s centerpiece powered by the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone comprehensive preventative subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure peak mechanical longevity and structural rigidity. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox delivers precise gate entry, feeding power through a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. Suspension kinematics remain within factory tolerances, featuring fresh bushings and optimal damping characteristics. The exterior finish is flawless, exhibiting zero oxidative stress or panel misalignment, while the undercarriage remains in a concourse-clean state. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning collector who demands atmospheric performance and mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
